text: Sea potato may refer to : *Colpomenia peregrina, a species of brown algae more commonly known as oyster thief or bladder weed *Leathesia marina, formerly Leathesia difformis, another species of brown algae more commonly known as sea cauliflower * Species of littoral sea urchins, especially heart urchins *Echinocardium cordatum, a specific species of urchin, commonly known as common heart urchin.
